sub_title: Honours Bachelor Student at University College Maastricht
summary:
I am an enthusiastic and persistent student, graduated from University College Maastricht (focusing on International Relations and Economics). I consider myself an empathic and positive individual, capable of being autonomous and efficiently working in a team. 

My main areas of interest are related to International Development and Human Rights. I am genuinely interested in deepening my knowledge regarding these subjects and pursuing the chance to belong to the community of internationally well-recognized organizations and companies. 

Other than my studies, I really like organizing, and I think that my skills in representing people would be helpful for any company.
